Im trying to make a auto totem script that moves totems into slot 9 and offhand to look like your legit double handing totems but I cant figure out how to make it bypass ``` def module double-hand-auto-totem
def desc "Custom Scripted Module"

on tick if input_active inventory {
    switch #totem
    wait 0.1 gui_quickmove #totem 9
    if off_holding #air {
        wait 0.3 gui_swap #totem
    }
}